OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain, this turning heavy at times. A
OL,7,Ffew limited brighter intervals in the
OL,8,Feast, where it could be quite warm.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA rather cloudy evening and
OL,11,Fnight with a few scattered showers,
OL,12,Fone or two on the heavy side. Patchy
OL,13,Fmist and fog developing around coasts
OL,14,Fthrough the night.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FVariable amounts of cloud
OL,17,Fwith afternoon showers developing,
OL,18,Fsome of which will be heavy with a
OL,19,Frisk of thunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
